  sentences:
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a6867dcfd3df9de39a47dd4cc225fb7, type: 2}
    text: Looks like normal jumpin' won't work here.
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a6867dcfd3df9de39a47dd4cc225fb7, type: 2}
    text: Luckily, you know how to dash by pressing the right mouse button.
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a6867dcfd3df9de39a47dd4cc225fb7, type: 2}
    text: Try dashing towards that wall stump over there.
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6a6867dcfd3df9de39a47dd4cc225fb7, type: 2}
    text: And don't bang your head!!!
